(5218, 337, 'apply_section_one_row_two_apply_section_one_row_two_text', 'If you or someone you know is interested in applying to be a homeowner through Habitat for Humanity, please consider our three criteria:\r\n\r\n1. Need for Housing\r\n2. Ability to Pay\r\n3. Willingness to Partner'),
